Welcome to "aim_texture_x_world_01"

Map created By El_Mexicano


This is an "AIM" map , with 12 slots in each team, 12 slots for the terrorists & 12 
slots for the counter-terroristes for  total of 24 slots!!!
The map is in shape of "X" , and the respawn points are at the extremity of the "X" ,which
means that there is 4 respawn points: each team begin face to face with 6 respawn entity per
respawn point
There is no aim , the only aim is to kill all players of the other team!
It's a "FUN" map , that's why all the creation of this map was based on the FUN side 
of the map , and that's why i've used the grey & orange textures like the ones you 
can find in "fy_blazin" or " texture_city " map (for those who know them)
There is many warpzone in this maps and invisible map in which ones you can walk !!!, i'll
let you find it yourself(if you want all the warpzone possible, contact me at the address 
www.hellzwindstaff.net)
Many sounds & lights effects

The .BSP file makes 13,6 MO, the .NAV file makes 684 ko 

Big thanks to the LoS*LaTiNoS production for their help & all the team for the help they gave me
